{"tid":1363827,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元 朗 大 樹 下 天 后 廟","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T08:54:22.000Z","uid":155431,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b125ddf5836353e176dee980d3cdddcf7d38470a","tid":1363827,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:50:08.000Z","msg":"大樹下天后廟是香港一所天后廟，位於新界元朗區十八鄉大旗嶺。該廟前方有一棵方圓達數百尺的大樹，因而得名。<br />\n<br />\n廟內的石碑可追溯至清朝乾隆51年（1786年），並先後於清朝咸豐、光緒年間和1962年颱風溫黛襲港後進行過大修。<br />\n<br />\n該廟有3殿，正殿奉祀天后；右殿奉祀文武二帝；左殿為英勇祠，奉祀抵抗1899年英國佔領新界而殉難的當地居民。"},{"pid":"a6409816a413f8868b7b7a83a6edfba608815ef1","tid":1363827,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:51:09.000Z","msg":"\\|/"},{"pid":"48bd623b9b3c56c2d5ab726f9e477a138c682f9d","tid":1363827,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"\\|/"},{"pid":"55df160a863185da9f4ae2707e99f3becba83270","tid":1363827,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=112303b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"},{"pid":"0cafbe33ec2063f636f42cf788de29a97eca186f","tid":1363827,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">[ 有方法 ] 揾人幫手個個星期六日都申請元朗遊行，等佢個個星期宵禁！！！&quot;</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363779</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpkuBjX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpkuBjX.gif&h=bdb422a9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}